Ready to personalize your NGINX container? Letâ€™s create a custom Docker image with your own web page!

ğŸ“‚ 1. Prepare Your Project Directory
Download or create an index.html file with your custom content.
Place it in your project directory.
ğŸ“„ 2. Create a Dockerfile
