Whatâ€™s happening here:

ğŸ› ï¸ FROM nginx:latest: Using the latest NGINX image as the base.
ğŸ“ COPY: Copies the custom index.html file to NGINXâ€™s document root.
ğŸ”“ EXPOSE 80: Exposes port 80 for web traffic.
ğŸ”¨ 3. Build and Tag the Custom Image
bash
Copy
Edit
